definitions.definition: The action of trying at something.
examples: We made an attempt to cross the stream, but didn’t manage.
This poem is much better than the feeble attempt of mine.
No matter how many failed attempts we made, we maintained a positive attitude and tried again and again until we succeeded.

definitions.definition: An assault or attack , especially an assassination attempt.
A substantial but unsuccessful effort (to commit a crime ).

main_definition: The action of trying at something.
secondary_definitions: An assault or attack , especially an assassination attempt.
( criminal law ) A substantial but unsuccessful effort (to commit a crime ).
